## Credits

This ESPHome external component is a fork of the original US-100 component by @redhoodie:
https://github.com/redhoodie/us100

This component gives access to the distance and temperature information of the famous
US-100 module from Adafruit Industries

This fork is maintained by @smogol66 for a garage door monitoring project using a XIAO ESP32-C6 and a US-100 ultrasonic sensor.